Package com.totsp.mavenplugin.gwt

Class Summary
AbstractGWTMojo Abstract Mojo for GWT-Maven.
BeanGeneratorMojo Generates client beans for the project (currently unsupported).
CompileMojo Invokes the GWTCompiler for the project source.
DebugMojo Extends the gwt goal and runs the project in the GWTShell with a debugger port hook (optionally suspended).
GWTMojo Runs the the project in the GWTShell for development.
GWTTestMojo Runs special (non surefire) test phase for GWTTestCase derived tests.
I18NMojo Creates I18N interfaces for constants and messages files.
MergeWebXmlMojo Merges GWT servlet elements into deployment descriptor (and non GWT servlets into shell).
ValidateMojo Validates the GWT source but does not compile.
WriteAllScripts Simply writes out all the scripts to the target folder.
